@startuml seq-08-document-upload
title POST /documents/upload — new document + version + enqueue ingest

actor "User" as U <<human>>
participant "Browser" as B <<browser>>
participant "Express\n/documents" as API <<service>>
participant "authenticateToken +\nrequireDocLibraryAccess +\nrequireManageDocumentsCapability" as MW <<service>>
participant "multer" as MU <<service>>
participant "Local storage" as FS <<service>>
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
queue "BullMQ\ndocument-ingest" as Q <<queue>>
participant "notifyDocumentCreated\n(async)" as N <<service>>

B -> API: POST /documents/upload\nmultipart (file + fields)

API -> MW: pre-handlers
alt Fails middleware / multer
  API --> B: 401 / 403 / 400
else OK
  API -> MU: upload.single("file")
  API -> API: Zod uploadMeta;\nresolveMimeType; sha256;\nallocateStorageKey
  API -> FS: saveUploadedFile(storageKey, buffer)
  API -> DB: $transaction:\n document.create (+ tags)\n documentVersion.create v1
  API -> Q: enqueueDocumentIngest(versionId)
  API -> DB: logDocumentAudit(CREATED)
  opt document.departmentId set
    API -> N: notifyDocumentCreated(...)\n.fire-and-forget .catch(log)
    N -> DB: createNotification + recipients\n(see seq-15)
  end
  API --> B: 201 { document, version }
end

note right of API
  Source: **apps/api/src/routes/documents.ts** (~76+),
  **enqueueDocumentIngest** in **jobs/documentIngest.ts**.
end note

@enduml
